      • fromVertex

        public static Embedding fromVertex(Vertex vertex,
                                   List<String> propertyKeys)
        Converts a Vertex into an Embedding. The resulting embedding has one entry containing the vertex id and one entry for each property value associated with the specified property keys (ordered by list order). Note that missing property values are represented by a PropertyValue.NULL_VALUE.
        Parameters:
        vertex - vertex to create embedding from
        propertyKeys - properties that will be stored in the embedding
        Returns:
        Embedding

      • fromEdge

        public static Embedding fromEdge(Edge edge,
                                 List<String> propertyKeys,
                                 boolean isLoop)
        Converts an Edge into an Embedding. The resulting embedding has three entries containing the source vertex id, the edge id and the target vertex id. Furthermore, the embedding has one entry for each property value associated with the specified property keys (ordered by list order). Note that missing property values are represented by a PropertyValue.NULL_VALUE.
        Parameters:
        edge - edge to create embedding from
        propertyKeys - properties that will be stored in the embedding
        isLoop - indicates if the edges is a loop
        Returns:
        Embedding

      • fromTriple

        public static Embedding fromTriple(Triple triple,
                                   List<String> sourcePropertyKeys,
                                   List<String> edgePropertyKeys,
                                   List<String> targetPropertyKeys,
                                   String sourceVertexVariable,
                                   String targetVertexVariable)
        Converts an Triple into an Embedding. The resulting embedding has two or three entries containing the source vertex id, the edge id and the target vertex id. Furthermore, the embedding has one entry for each property value associated with the specified property keys (ordered by source properties, edge properties, target properties in list order). Note that missing property values are represented by a PropertyValue.NULL_VALUE.
        Parameters:
        triple - triple to create embedding from
        sourcePropertyKeys - source properties that will be stored in the embedding
        edgePropertyKeys - edge properties that will be stored in the embedding
        targetPropertyKeys - target properties that will be stored in the embedding
        sourceVertexVariable - variable of the source vertex
        targetVertexVariable - variable of the target vertex
        Returns:
        Embedding
